				<td colspan="2"><span>This ability allows for further improvements in the use of all instrument and singing types.
<br />

<br />
What on earth does this mean, I have it a level 3 but can see no effect.
<br />

<br />
Tested on a variety of songs, but as always resist songs are the of easiest to see differeneces on.
<br />

<br />
I'd like to see my dots doing more damage or psalm of veeshan provide more resists, but it just aint happening.
<br />

<br />
So what is this skill for????
<br />

<br />
iRid</span></td>
